{"tid":1463263,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Evo X 手波","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:44:38.000Z","uid":224444,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3f02b8ec7eab035fa26d3c13a113f58d56d43ca1","tid":1463263,"uid":224444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:33:34.000Z","msg":"本身諗住打算日本bid部原裝翻黎<br />\n貪佢直板無俾人改到亂哂<br />\n但依家yen升到把把聲 意欲大減<br />\n見28 car放緊部白09 evo x<br />\n好似都企理靚仔<br />\n但改左都一堆野 唔係太識<br />\n因為有車位 部車打算都長keep <br />\n所以唔想買到問題車<br />\n希望巴打指點下<br />\n<br />\nHKS Hipermax IV SP Coilovers<br />\nBlitz Sus Power Air Filter<br />\nMonster Sport Intercooler Pipe<br />\nMonster Sport Suction Pipe<br />\nHKS SSQV4 BOV<br />\nExcedy Stage 1 Clutch<br />\nTomei Downpipe<br />\nTomei Test Pipe&nbsp;<br />\nTomei Mid Pipe + Muffler<br />\nAMS 3.5&quot; Intercooler<br />\nGreddy Profec OLED Boost Controller<br />\nDW65C 265LPH Fuel Pump<br />\nTurbosmart 1.5bar turbo actuator<br />\nAP Racing 5000R CP9660 (跟回原裝Brembo)<br />\nParagon 370mm brake disc (跟回原裝碟)<br />\nWinmax W5 (100-750 temp) brake pad<br />\nTE37SL 18x9.5J +22<br />\nRE71R 265/35/18 (Less than 1000km driven)<br />\nJun Style Carbon Front Lip<br />\nHKS Spark Plugs (changed 1000km ago)<br />\n<br />\n上面一堆野 都係識睇一半到<br />\n想問如果之後跟翻會唔會好難跟?<br />\n有改bov roadblock是咪好易奶野?<br />\nevo x上架有無話邊間車房出名熟手d?<br />\n有無咩要跟咁<br />\n唔該哂巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8291dcd74ab70c2e1aa4dc105db1f49137b703b3","tid":1463263,"uid":149908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"有部現貨，岩不岩"},{"pid":"c3c0208014f1b22c07778bbf51564048b6438499","tid":1463263,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"09就買部九代好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c3e369de42087377c28f7f7298db6b28f4b7ef","tid":1463263,"uid":224444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"829